<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/33027279">为什么人有时会出现「更容易向陌生人展示真实想法」的情况？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="5417009" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"><b>本题来自知乎圆桌 »</b><b><a href="http://www.zhihu.com/roundtable/loneliness" class="internal">谁不孤独</a>，欢迎关注讨论。</b></div>


</div>
